description:
When using StreamableHTTPServerTransport, enable DNS rebinding protection for security:

```typescript
new StreamableHTTPServerTransport({
  enableDnsRebindingProtection: true,
  allowedHosts: ['localhost', '127.0.0.1'],
  allowedOrigins: ['http://localhost:3000']
});
```

This prevents malicious websites from making requests to the local MCP server.
